Daily Word Privacy Policy
Last Updated: February 2, 2023
Introduction
Daily Word is committed to protecting the privacy of its users. This Privacy Policy explains what information we collect, how we use it, and the steps we take to ensure its security. We encourage you to read this Privacy Policy carefully.
Information Collection
Daily Word collects information from its users in several ways, including through the use of our iOS app. The information we collect may include:
Personal Information: We may collect personal information, such as your name, email address, and any other information you choose to provide.
Device Information: We may collect information about your device, including its operating system, IP address, and device ID.
Log Information: When you use Daily Word, we may collect information about your usage of the app, such as the pages you visit and the actions you take.
Use of Information
Daily Word uses the information we collect to provide and improve our services, including to:
Provide customer support and respond to your inquiries.
Send you updates and notifications about Daily Word.
Analyze usage and trends to improve the app.
Comply with applicable laws and regulations.
Security
Daily Word takes reasonable measures to protect the security of the information we collect. We use secure servers and encryption to protect sensitive information, and we regularly review our security measures to ensure that they remain effective. However, please note that no method of transmitting or storing information is completely secure, and we cannot guarantee the security of any information we collect.
Third-Party Services
Daily Word may use third-party services to provide certain services, such as hosting, analytics, and customer support. These third-party services may collect information about you and your usage of Daily Word. Please refer to the privacy policies of these third-party services for more information.
Changes to this Privacy Policy
Daily Word may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. If we make any material changes, we will notify you by posting the updated policy on our website or through the app.
Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about these Terms and Conditions, please contact us at
support@thedailywordapp.com
